name: LAKSHAY GUPTA

top_projects.name: MangaBot
top_projects.description: A Telegram bot powered by Python and Docker, enabling users to search for manga titles from "manganato.com" directly within Telegram. Leveraging the Telegram Bot API and telebot library, it offers a seamless search experience

top_projects.name: flutter_demo_apps
top_projects.description: A curated repository showcasing a variety of Flutter demo applications, highlighting different features and functionalities of the Flutter framework.

ilakshaygupt/Soundly-iOS.summary: Significant updates to Soundly iOS, including integration with SoundlyWatchOs Watch App, setup screens, navigation, song queue management, player state management, and various bug fixes.

ilakshaygupt/CODETION-BACKEND.summary: Further development on CODETION-BACKEND includes changes to Celery, PostgreSQL configuration, Docker file modifications, and reversion of permissions and authentication changes.

ilakshaygupt/zulip.summary: Recent updates in Zulip primarily focus on improvements in features like composebox typeahead, Django API event handling, channel subscription notifications, help documentation, and file uploading.

Somgupta786/ensite.summary: Key update to Ensite involves data updates for ASICS2K25.

ilakshaygupt/otakusama-frontend.summary: Recent update in Otakusama-frontend mainly removes the deprecated UnmodifiableUint8ListView.

profile_summary:
Renowned software developer LAKSHAY GUPTA is a highly skilled and accomplished technologist, leveraging expertise in C++, Swift, and Python to drive innovation and deliver exceptional results. With a strong professional network comprising 33 followers and a portfolio boasting 41 public repositories, Gupta demonstrates a steadfast commitment to collaboration and knowledge-sharing, showcasing a breadth of experience and technical prowess.

A seasoned developer with a passion for solving complex problems, Gupta brings a unique combination of technical acumen and strategic insight to every project. With a proven track record of delivering high-quality solutions, Gupta is a trusted partner for businesses seeking to harness the full potential of software development. By staying at the forefront of emerging trends and technologies, Gupta consistently delivers cutting-edge solutions that drive business success and exceed client expectations.
